  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Product Reviewer / Quality Feedback Associate",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Job Description</strong></h3><p>We are looking for a detail-oriented <strong>Product Reviewer</strong> to evaluate products, provide feedback, and help improve product quality and user experience. This role is ideal for individuals who are observant, articulate, and enjoy trying new products.</p><p>No prior experience is required, as training and guidance will be provided.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Test and evaluate products according to provided guidelines</p></li><li><p>Provide clear and honest feedback on product quality and usability</p></li><li><p>Document observations, ratings, and reviews accurately</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the team to share insights and improve product offerings</p></li><li><p>Follow company procedures and standards for product testing</p></li><li><p>Participate in occasional product review meetings or discussions</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum 18 years old</p></li><li><p>Good command of English, both written and spoken</p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and analytical skills</p></li><li><p>Comfortable using and evaluating different types of products</p></li><li><p>Ability to provide clear and objective feedback</p></li><li><p>Responsible, reliable, and able to meet deadlines</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We Offer</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Monthly salary <strong>SGD 2,500 – 3,200</strong></p></li><li><p>Training and guidance provided</p></li><li><p>Hands-on exposure to product evaluation and quality assurance</p></li><li><p>Supportive and collaborative work environment</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for growth within product testing and quality roles</p></li></ul>",
